        ## Sentiment Lexicons
        ```python
        In [1]: import sentlex
         
        In [2]: SWN = sentlex.SWN3Lexicon()
         
        In [3]: SWN.getadjective('good')
        Out[3]: (0.6190476190476191, 0.0)
         
        In [4]: SWN.getverb('amuse')
        Out[4]: (0.75, 0.0)
         
        In [5]: SWN.getadjective('terrible')
        Out[5]: (0.0, 0.65625)
        ```
        
